data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. “MOTIVATED SELLERS”!!!!  Bring all offers This exquisite 3 bedrooms, 4 bath Pool home with an office is situated in the gated community of Covington Cove, within the city limits of Winter Haven. This sophisticated stylish home features Custom Cabinetry, Granite Countertops, and a Breakfast Bar, with Pool views from the Living, Family, and Dining areas. The house has new Roof, Pool Screen, newer Hot Water Heater & Appliances, Engineered Wood Floors, Custom Molding, and a Gas Fireplace in the Living Room. The pool is heated and has a hot tub and a full Bath. The Master suite includes a walk-in closet with Dual Sinks, accent Molding, a Garden Tub, and a Glass Shower. Additionally, there's a bonus room upstairs with a Wet Bar, perfect for a game/media/party area. The attic is floored, and there's a large covered and uncovered patio for entertaining. The home also has Double Pane Insulated Anderson Windows, a side load garage, mature landscaping, and many more amenities & comforts to offer. The elegant home is within minutes from many restaurants, shopping, medical, and Legoland.  The Community of Covington Cove is along Lake Otis Chain, where Large Mouth Bass can be caught. All measurements are approximate and must be verified by buyer(s).
